Label: Amphibian Name
Description: Represents the scientific or common name of an amphibian species in the KN-Wildlife knowledge network.

Label: Bird Name
Description: Represents the scientific or common name of a bird species in the KN-Wildlife knowledge network.

Label: Location
Description: A geographic place or spatial region where wildlife observations occur.

Label: Date
Description: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource.

Label: Label
Description: A human-readable name or title for a resource.

Label: Subject Of
Description: A CreativeWork or Event about this Thing. Links a resource to content that has it as the subject matter.

Label: Observed At
Description: Relates a wildlife species observation to the geographic location where it was observed.

Label: Observed Times
Description: The number of times or frequency that a particular species has been observed at a location.
